# Privacy Policy

## Last updated: [04/18/2024]

### Introduction
This document clarifies the privacy practices of the game "Bouncing Around". Our policy is to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect while you use our game.

### Information Collected
"Bouncing Around" only collects the language of your device, but advertisements served by third parties may collect data such as your IP, device type, device identification number, geographic location, and other information that allows you to customize the advertisements shown to you. you.
Our advertising partners:
- Google AdMob (Privacy Policy: [https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/](https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/))

### Information Use and Information Sharing
We only use the device's language to change the game language, and the data collected by advertisements follows the Privacy Policy mentioned above

### Consent to Personalized Advertising

By using our game, you agree to the use and collection of your information for personalized advertising purposes.

### Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Therefore, we advise you to review this page periodically for any changes. These changes are effective immediately upon being posted on this page.

### Contact
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, please do not hesitate to contact us at picotecontact@gmail.com

